questions.questionText:
What is the behavior of the following asynchronous script?

```js
setTimeout(() => console.log('A'), 0);
Promise.resolve().then(() => console.log('B'));
console.log('C');
```

What value will the following block return?

```js
const obj = {
  val: 42,
  getVal: () => this.val
};
console.log(obj.getVal());
```
